### Create a product
POST http://localhost:5000/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Gaming Laptop",
  "price": 1299.99,
  "description": "High performance gaming laptop with RTX 4060",
  "category": "electronics",
  "inStock": true
}

### Create another product
POST http://localhost:5000/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "JavaScript Book",
  "price": 39.99,
  "description": "Complete guide to JavaScript",
  "category": "books",
  "inStock": true
}

### Get all products
GET http://localhost:5000/api/products

### Get products by category
GET http://localhost:5000/api/products?category=electronics

### Get single product (replace ID with actual)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/products/YOUR_PRODUCT_ID

### Update product (replace ID with actual)
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/products/YOUR_PRODUCT_ID
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "price": 1199.99,
  "inStock": false
}

### Delete product (replace ID with actual)
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/products/YOUR_PRODUCT_ID